   20: -module(groups_11_SUITE).

   24: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").

   26: %%====================================================================
   27: %% COMMON TEST CALLBACK FUNCTIONS
   28: %%====================================================================
   29: 
   30: suite() ->
   31:     [{timetrap,{minutes,1}}].
   32: 
   33: groups() ->
   34:     [ 
   35:       {test_group_1a, [testcase_1a,testcase_1b]},
   36:       
   37:       {test_group_1b, [], [testcase_1a,testcase_1b]},
   38:       
   39:       {test_group_2, [], [testcase_2a,
   40: 			  
   41: 			  {test_group_3, [], [testcase_3a, 
   42: 					      testcase_3b]},			  
   43: 			  testcase_2b]},
   44:       
   45:       {test_group_4, [{test_group_5, [], [testcase_5a,
   46: 					  
   47: 					  {group, test_group_6},
   48: 					  
   49: 					  testcase_5b]}]},
   50:       
   51:       {test_group_6, [{group, test_group_7}]},
   52:       
   53:       {test_group_7, [testcase_7a,testcase_7b]}      
   54:      ].
   55: 	    
   56: all() -> 
   57:     [testcase_1,
   58:      {group, test_group_1a},
   59:      {group, test_group_1b},
   60:      testcase_2,
   61:      {group, test_group_2},
   62:      testcase_3,
   63:      {group, test_group_4}].
   64: 
   65: %% this func only for internal test purposes
   66: grs_and_tcs() ->
   67:     {[
   68:       test_group_1a, test_group_1b,
   69:       test_group_2, test_group_3,
   70:       test_group_4, test_group_5,
   71:       test_group_6, test_group_7
   72:      ],	    
   73:      [
   74:       testcase_1, 
   75:       testcase_1a, testcase_1b,
   76:       testcase_2, 
   77:       testcase_2a, testcase_2b,
   78:       testcase_3a, testcase_3b,
   79:       testcase_3,
   80:       testcase_5a, testcase_5b,
   81:       testcase_7a, testcase_7b
   82:      ]}.
   83: 
   84: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   85: %% Suite Configuration
   86: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   87: 
   88: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   89:     [{suite,init}|Config].
   90: 
   91: end_per_suite(Config) ->
   92:     init = ?config(suite,Config).
   93: 
   94: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   95: %% Group Configuration
   96: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   97: 
   98: init_per_group(Group, Config) ->
   99:     [{name,Group}] = ?config(tc_group_properties,Config),
  100:     {Grs,_} = grs_and_tcs(),
  101:     case lists:member(Group, Grs) of
  102: 	true ->
  103: 	    ct:comment(Group),
  104: 	    init = ?config(suite,Config),
  105: 	    [{Group,Group} | Config];
  106: 	false ->
  107: 	    ct:fail({bad_group,Group})
  108:     end.
  109: 
  110: end_per_group(Group, Config) ->
  111:     {Grs,_} = grs_and_tcs(),
  112:     case lists:member(Group, Grs) of
  113: 	true ->
  114: 	    ct:comment(Group),
  115: 	    init = ?config(suite,Config),
  116: 	    Group = ?config(Group,Config),
  117: 	    ok;
  118: 	false ->
  119: 	    ct:fail({bad_group,Group})
  120:     end.
  121: 
  122: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  123: %% Testcase Configuration
  124: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  125: 
  126: init_per_testcase(TestCase, Config) ->
  127:     {_,TCs} = grs_and_tcs(),
  128:     case lists:member(TestCase, TCs) of
  129: 	true ->	    
  130: 	    init = ?config(suite,Config),
  131: 	    [{TestCase,TestCase} | Config];
  132: 	false ->
  133: 	    ct:fail({unknown_testcase,TestCase})
  134:     end.
  135: 
  136: end_per_testcase(TestCase, Config) ->
  137:     {_,TCs} = grs_and_tcs(),
  138:     case lists:member(TestCase, TCs) of
  139: 	true ->	    
  140: 	    init = ?config(suite,Config),
  141: 	    TestCase = ?config(TestCase,Config),
  142: 	    ok;
  143: 	false ->
  144: 	    ct:fail({unknown_testcase,TestCase})
  145:     end.
  146: 
  147:
